sols.text: Of course. What do you need?
I’d like to change my seat.
I see. Is there something wrong?
لا، لكني أود الجلوس بجانب صديقتي.
No, but I’d like to sit next to my friend.
I don't know. But she's sitting over there.
صحيح. سأتأكد إذا كان المقعد الذي بجانبها مُتاح.
Right. I'll check if the seat next to her is available.
كل شيء على ما يرام. تستطعن الجلوس معًا الآن.
All is good. You can sit together now.
Yes, when will the plane take off?
